So, I switched it to the default

00:34:33.936 --> 00:34:36.016
background color, and now

00:34:36.146 --> 00:34:37.076
everything looks great.

00:34:38.156 --> 00:34:39.246
And while we're here on this

00:34:39.286 --> 00:34:40.485
text view, I'd like to go

00:34:40.485 --> 00:34:41.626
through some of the colors in

00:34:41.626 --> 00:34:43.505
play here that are dynamic

00:34:43.686 --> 00:34:45.136
system colors that also may be

00:34:45.136 --> 00:34:45.846
useful to you.

00:34:46.396 --> 00:34:50.746
First, there's textColor, which

00:34:50.746 --> 00:34:52.656
is switching between black and

